3231 /// A recipe to combine multiple recipes into a single 'expression' recipe,
3232 /// which should be considered a single entity for cost-modeling and transforms.
3233 /// The recipe needs to be 'decomposed', i.e. replaced by its individual
3234 /// expression recipes, before execute. The individual expression recipes are
3235 /// completely disconnected from the def-use graph of other recipes not part of
