2204 ///    canonical or derived induction.
2205 ///  * VPWidenPointerInductionRecipe: Generate vector and scalar values for a
2206 ///    pointer induction. Produces either a vector PHI per-part or scalar values
2207 ///    per-lane based on the canonical induction.
